        {
          "id": "relative_clauses",
          "title": "Relative Clauses (der, die, das)",
          "explanation": "Relative clauses give more info about a noun. The relative pronoun (der/die/das/den/dem) matches the gender/case of the noun. Verb goes to the END.",
